  "A genomics researcher has gene expression data: 20,000 genes measured across 200 patients. She applies PCA and plots the first two principal components. The plot shows two distinct clusters. What has she discovered?": "",
  "Exactly two genes are important, particularly regarding data according to conventional analysis": "",
